data.description: JUST IN TIME FOR SUMMER!! Wonderful POOL home in the Woodlands Subdivision just off of E.E. Williamson and Markham Woods Rd. HUGE fenced yard, screen enclosed porch and lots of beautiful shade trees! This block home is a 4 bed, 2 bath with REAL wood floors and ceramic tile. Partially updated with Newer Kitchen, complete with cabinets, counter-top and appliances, Newer Hall Bath cabinet and counter-top, Newer Roof and the Pool Resurfaced a few years ago. Inside utility room with room for storage, family room with wood burning fireplace, ceiling fans and all the charm that comes with having a home in The Woodlands.  Great Neighborhood, Great Seminole County Schools, Great Location and an even better price!! Flood Insurance is required.
